Yang Xingzhong (chè), whose real name is Jiang Bo, was born in the year of the sheep, during the month of the sheep, and grew up among the grasses of the sheep. He felt that he was perfectly suited for that environment, which is why he was named Yang Xingzhong; people also call him “Uncle Yang”.
